1. Executive Summary

Dario Amodei does not know the author. He does not know almost anyone in the open-source AI community. He does not know the ordinary people, independent researchers, small laboratories, engineers, students, hobbyists, accountants, teachers, or disabled users who may wish to build, inspect, fine-tune, or run AI systems outside closed corporate platforms.

